# Large model files (keep only what's needed)
**/bench marks/
**/mnn models/
**/onnx models/
**/runs/
**/TensorRT/
**/torchscript models/

# Keep only the optimized OpenVINO model (its files must be explicitly
# re-included after ignored parent paths).
!app/ai_models/model N/
!app/ai_models/model N/openvino models/
!app/ai_models/model N/openvino models/best_int8_openvino_model/
!app/ai_models/model N/openvino models/best_int8_openvino_model/**

